@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_irhvvg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(v2)
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.90)) + v2)
    v0 = ((v1 + tmp) * (0.87 + (tmp + 0.39 / v1 + 0.59)))
    tmp = ((tmp + v0) * (0.65 * 0.89))
    data[tid] = v0
